////How to collect visitors information (name, email, phone) to call customer later to sale his product//////////////

To collect visitor info like name, email, and phone number on Facebook / Meta and let your client call them later, use Lead Generation Ads (also called Instant Forms).

This ad opens a form inside Facebook or Instagram, so users can submit quickly.

Steps to create Lead Ads:
Go to Meta Ads Manager
Click Create Campaign
Select objective → Leads
Campaign Level
Choose Manual Leads Campaign or Instant Forms
Name your campaign
Ad Set Level

Set these options:

Conversion Location

Choose Instant Forms

Facebook Page

Select your client’s page

Audience

Country / city / area
Age
Gender
Interests / behavior

Budget

Daily or Lifetime budget

Placements

Automatic placements recommended
Ad Level

Create ad with:

Image / video
Primary text
Headline
CTA button like Apply Now, Get Quote, Learn More
Create Instant Form

In form settings:

Add fields:
✅ Full Name
✅ Email
✅ Phone Number

Optional:

Address
Custom questions

Example custom question:
“When should we call you?”

Privacy Policy

Facebook requires a privacy policy link in Lead Form.

Example:
https://yourclientwebsite.com/privacy-policy

Thank You Screen

After submit, show:
“Thanks! Our team will contact you soon.”

Button options:

Visit website
Call business


