/////How to download leads from Meta Ads Manager?//////////////////////////

To download leads from Meta Ads Manager:

Method 1: From Ads Manager
Open Meta Ads Manager
Select the Lead Ad Campaign
Click the Ads tab
Find your ad and click Results or On-Facebook Leads
Click Download / Export New Leads
Choose format:
CSV
Excel (.xlsx)
Save file to your device
Method 2: From Facebook Page
Open your client’s Facebook Page
Go to Publishing Tools or Professional Dashboard
Click Instant Forms / Lead Center
Select the form
Click Download CSV
Method 3: From Meta Business Suite
Open Meta Business Suite
Go to All Tools
Open Instant Forms or Leads Center
Select form
Click Download
Important:

Leads are available for only 90 days on Meta, so download regularly.


